ntre d’AMP Procreo La Soie Lyon-Villeurbanne. Ce centre innovant propose un accompagnement global des couples concernés par l’infertilité, par une équipe interdisciplinaire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aMedicine. 4aObstetrician gynecology. 4aPublic Health. 7aMEDICAL / Neuroscience.2bisacsh1 aGodefroy, Anne-Sophie, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020z978311075640140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2273-740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759822737423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759822737/original  a978-3-11-075640-1  EDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020c2016d2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK